{"prompt": "Generate a website for a video game studio. The website should be elegant and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Crimson Studios</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #A52A2A; /* Brownish-red */\n            --secondary-color: #8B0000; /* Dark red */\n            --text-color: #FFFFFF;\n            --background-color: #1a1a1a;\n            --accent-color: #D3D3D3; /* Light gray */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3.5rem;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);\n        }\n\n        main {\n            padding: 3rem 1rem;\n            max-width: 960px;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);\n        }\n\n        section {\n            margin-bottom: 3rem;\n            padding: 2rem;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            background-color: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.8);\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n            font-size: 2rem;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-color);\n            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;\n        }\n\n        p {\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .game-gallery {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 1.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .game-item {\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .game-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(165, 42, 42, 0.4); /* Reddish glow */\n        }\n\n        .game-item img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .game-item-info {\n            padding: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .game-item-info h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            font-size: 1.4rem;\n        }\n\n        .game-item-info p {\n            font-size: 0.95rem;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem 1rem;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n            margin-top: 3rem;\n            box-shadow: 0 -4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 0.5rem;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        footer a:hover {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        /* Responsive adjustments */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5rem;\n            }\n\n            h2 {\n                font-size: 1.8rem;\n            }\n\n            main {\n                padding: 2rem 0.5rem;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Crimson Studios</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <main>\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>Crimson Studios is a passionate indie game development team dedicated to crafting immersive and unforgettable interactive experiences. We believe in the power of storytelling and innovative gameplay to transport players to new worlds.</p>\n            <p>Founded with a love for classic and modern gaming, we strive to push the boundaries of what's possible, delivering high-quality titles that resonate with our audience.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"games\">\n            <h2>Our Games</h2>\n            <div class=\"game-gallery\">\n                <div class=\"game-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/8B0000/FFFFFF?text=Game+One\" alt=\"Game One Screenshot\">\n                    <div class=\"game-item-info\">\n                        <h3>Crimson Echoes</h3>\n                        <p>A dark fantasy RPG where choices shape destiny. Explore a world on the brink of collapse.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"game-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/A52A2A/FFFFFF?text=Game+Two\" alt=\"Game Two Screenshot\">\n                    <div class=\"game-item-info\">\n                        <h3>Scarlet Velocity</h3>\n                        <p>A fast-paced futuristic racing game with intense competition and stunning visuals.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"game-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/800000/FFFFFF?text=Game+Three\" alt=\"Game Three Screenshot\">\n                    <div class=\"game-item-info\">\n                        <h3>Ruby's Ascent</h3>\n                        <p>A charming puzzle-platformer with a heartwarming story and unique mechanics.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>We love hearing from our community! For press inquiries, business opportunities, or just to say hello, please reach out:</p>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n                Email: <a href=\"mailto:info@crimsonstudios.com\" style=\"color: var(--text-color); text-decoration: underline;\">info@crimsonstudios.com</a>\n            </p>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n                Follow us:\n                <a href=\"#\" aria-label=\"Twitter\">Twitter</a> |\n                <a href=\"#\" aria-label=\"Facebook\">Facebook</a> |\n                <a href=\"#\" aria-label=\"Discord\">Discord</a>\n            </p>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Crimson Studios. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>\n            <a href=\"#about\">About</a> |\n            <a href=\"#games\">Games</a> |\n            <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n        </p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}